1D X pass 4H pass pass pass
[BCFlags "1f"]
[RotationNote "Board 4, chOption: W, chBasis: N, basisKind:Declarer, nOption:3, nBasis: 0, nRot: 3, useStandardVul: true"]
[Category "Partnership Bidding"]
[Difficulty "intermediate"]
[SkillPath "partnership_bidding/overcalls"]
[Student "S"]
{EAST has a very minimum Takeout Double of 1\D. But what it lacks 
in strength, it makes up for with perfect distribution.

WEST has 13 points and only wants to play in one contract, 4\H.

EAST passes happily.}

